readings.message: Intercepted whisper in mess: "[WHISPER] ROUGHNECK: Pike is losing it."
AUDIT COMPLETE: 2 anomalies detected (1 spoof, 1 fabrication). INTEGRITY COMPROMISED.
[SENSOR] DORMS: environmental readings conflict with expected baseline. Discrepancy unresolved.
[!!! STELLAR OBSERVATORY !!!] Anomalous stellar activity detected.
[!!! CME INCOMING !!!] Coronal mass ejection detected. Brace for impact.
[!!! IMPACT !!!] Solar flare hit. Sensors offline. Comms degraded.
VERIFY: Addressing crew concern â€” "engineer intends to check system logs". Evidence cross-referenced. Doubt cleared.
